<p><b>20) Quarterly Financial Information (Unaudited)</b></p>
<p>Each of the quarters includes 13 weeks, except for the fourth
quarter of 1995 which includes 14 weeks. Earnings per share amounts
for each quarter are required to be computed independently and may
not equal the amount computed for the total year. </p>
